<p class = "body-1">| [BBa_K3755014](http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_K3755014) | NFAT-RE+minP+EGFP                                           | To prove that the calcium signal activates downstream gene expression. |</p>
<p class = "body-1">| [BBa_K3755016](http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_K3755016) | CMV enhancer+CMV promoter+mPiezo1+mRuby2+bGH PolyA signal   | To express mPiezo1 in mammalian cells.                       |</p>
<p class = "body-1">| [BBa_K3755017](http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_K3755017) | CMV enhancer+CMV promoter+mPiezo1.1+mRuby2+bGH PolyA signal | To express mPiezo1.1 in mammalian cells.                     |</p>
<p class = "body-1">| [BBa_K3755023](http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_K3755023) | CMV enhancer+CMV promoter+IL2-AlgH-EGFP+SV40 PolyA signal   | To express IL2-AlgH-EGFP.                                    |</p>
